GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于红海延误，折扣商 Pepco 提前订购圣诞节发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/discounter-pepco-ordering-earlier-christmas-shipments-amid-red-sea-delays-2024-07-11/</link><description>欧洲折扣零售商 Pepco 集团老板周四表示，正从中国提前订购圣诞节货物，以确保在关键的节日交易期间及时交货。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/discounter-pepco-ordering-earlier-christmas-shipments-amid-red-sea-delays-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>大众旗下 MAN 和 E.ON 联手为电动卡车充电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</link><description>德国能源公司 E.ON 和大众汽车子公司 MAN Truck &amp;amp; Bus 周四表示，计划从今年开始建立泛欧洲卡车充电网络。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着美国降息押注的巩固，亚洲外汇空头有所缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于对美联储今年至少两次降息的预期不断上升以及美元走软提振了风险情绪，大多数亚洲货币的空头头寸有所缓解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:38:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国全会交付的政策议程因目标相互冲突而受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国领导人将在下周举行的备受期待的会议上寻求为经济注入信心，但相互冲突的目标，例如在削减债务的同时促进增长，可能意味着在实施变革方面进展甚微。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>央行为何推出新的现金管理工具？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国央行本周推出了一种新的现金管理工具，即临时债券回购协议和逆回购，增加了各种公开市场操作，并创造了可能成为重要利率指标的工具。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:04:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>全球储备经理对经济增长持乐观态度，但担心政治</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-reserve-managers-upbeat-growth-worry-about-politics-2024-07-11/</link><description>周四发布的年度调查显示，央行储备经理普遍对世界经济前景持乐观态度，他们表示，地缘政治冲突升级是全球经济面临的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-reserve-managers-upbeat-growth-worry-about-politics-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：IBAT在锂行业率先将新提取技术商业化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-industry-first-ibat-commercializes-new-extraction-technology-2024-07-11/</link><description>作为全球清洁能源转型的一个里程碑，国际电池金属公司成为第一家采用新型过滤技术商业化生产锂的公司，这一举措预计将带来更便宜、更快速的电动汽车电池金属供应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-industry-first-ibat-commercializes-new-extraction-technology-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国私营公司i-Space的火箭发射失败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/launch-rocket-chinese-private-firm-i-space-fails-2024-07-11/</link><description>官方新华社称，中国私营航天公司i-Space开发的双曲线一号火箭周四发射失败。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/launch-rocket-chinese-private-firm-i-space-fails-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>在美国通胀数据公布之前，股市创下历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-11/</link><description>世界股市周四创下历史新高，交易员倒计时美国数据，预计该数据将显示通胀放缓，并为美联储最早于 9 月份开始期待已久的降息周期铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:54:03 GM